{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 54,
  "title": "第五十四章（修觀）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "善建者不拔，"
    },
    {
      "text": "善抱者不脫，"
    },
    {
      "text": "子孫祭祀不輟。"
    },
    {
      "text": "修之於身，其德乃真，"
    },
    {
      "text": "修之於家，其德乃餘，"
    },
    {
      "text": "修之於鄉，其德乃長，"
    },
    {
      "text": "修之於國，其德乃豐，"
    },
    {
      "text": "修之於天下，其德乃普。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故以身觀身，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以家觀家，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以鄉觀鄉，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以國觀國，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以天下觀天下。"
    },
    {
      "text": "吾何以知天下之然哉，以此。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "建，立也。善以道立身立國者，不可得引而拔之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善以道抱精神者，終不可拔引解脫。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "為人子孫能修道如是，長生不死，世世以久，祭祀先祖，宗廟無絕時。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "修道於身，愛氣養神，益壽延年。其德如是，乃為真人。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "修道於家，父慈子孝，兄友弟順，夫信妻貞。 其德如是，乃有餘慶及於來世子孫。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "修道於鄉，尊敬長老，愛養幼少，教誨愚鄙。 其德如是，乃無不覆及也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "修道於國，則君信臣忠，仁義自生，禮樂自興，政平無私。 其德如是，乃為豐厚也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人主修道於天下，不言而化，不教而治，下之應上，信如影響。 其德如是，乃為普博。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以修道之身，觀不修道之身，孰亡孰存也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以修道之家，觀不修道之家。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以修道之鄉，觀不修道之鄉也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以修道之國，觀不修道之國也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以修道之主，觀不修道之主也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "老子言，吾何知天下修道者昌，背道者亡。以此五事觀而知之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
